# Debugging Strategy

## Error Analysis
- Identify 3-5 likely causes
- Log assumptions
- Validate variables
- Check state flow
- Review data structure

## Logging
- Structured log format
- Error boundaries
- Performance metrics
- User actions
- System events

## Testing
- Unit tests
- Integration tests
- E2E tests
- Performance tests
- Accessibility tests

## Monitoring
- Error tracking
- Performance monitoring
- User feedback
- API health checks
- Storage metrics

## Recovery
- Graceful degradation
- Retry mechanisms
- Fallback UI
- Data recovery
- State restoration 